# Security Policy — Trackr AI Hub

## Overview

This document describes the security posture, vulnerability management process, and audit procedures for the **Trackr** application (React 19 + Vite, deployed on Vercel).

- **Repository**: [andrea-ai992/trackr-ai-hub](https://github.com/andrea-ai992/trackr-ai-hub)
- **Production URL**: https://trackr-app-nu.vercel.app
- **Last Security Audit**: 2025-06-17
- **Audit Tool**: npm audit (built-in)
- **Node Requirement**: >= 18.0.0
- **npm Requirement**: >= 9.0.0

---

## Supported Versions

| Version | Supported          | Notes                        |
|---------|--------------------|------------------------------|
| 1.x     | YES                | Current production branch    |
| 0.x     | NO                 | Legacy — no security patches |

